ygData.messageBody:
Just thought I'd "share" with you a site that has the
best collection of maps for zones I have ever seen.
When I first joined the many lists I am on, I asked if
anyone had a map of the Freeport Sewers. Well, I just
stumbled upon it, and many more that I have never seen
before.
If you hate spoilers and want to learn an area by
experiencing it, don't go to the site.
I have yet to get a character over 6th level due to
boredome with a class, and hate running through an area
that I know knothing about and end up getting lost and
walking into 3 Mummies and 2 Zombies at 5th level (has
happened, just after a repop. :( ).
anyway, the site:

http://empty.com/rangers/maps/

I have new respect for Rangers. This group has their
act together.

--
Artimis
2nd Rank Enchanter
Bertoxxulous
